# Title: Suspicious Control Panel DLL Load
# Author: Florian Roth (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2017-04-15
# Level: high
# Description: Detects suspicious Rundll32 execution from control.exe as used by Equation Group and Exploit Kits
# MITRE Tactic: Uncategorized
# Tags: attack.stealth, attack.t1218.011
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_rundll32_susp_control_dll_load.yml

Image="*\\rundll32.exe" OR OriginalFileName="RUNDLL32.EXE" ParentImage="*\\System32\\control.exe" NOT CommandLine="*Shell32.dll*"